    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines a YANG data module that can be used to
   configure and manage OSPF Segment Routing.  It also defines a module
   for management of Signaling Maximum SID Depth (MSD) Using OSPF.  The
   modules are based on YANG 1.1 as defined in RFC 7950 and conform to
   the Network Management Datastore Architecture (NDMA) as described in
   RFC 8342.

	 </t>
